/installation  /docs/installation  301

# Machine-readable surfaces return a real 404 (not the SPA HTML shell) for a
# wrong/guessed name, so an agent gets a parseable "not found" instead of silently
# reading HTML as markdown/JSON. Static assets take precedence over these rules, so
# every real .md/.json still serves 200 — only missing paths fall through here.
/llms/*     /llms-404.md   404
/context/*  /llms-404.md   404
/r/*        /r-404.json    404
